chuckeles.sstasker.model.parts

Class OxygenGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • chuckeles.sstasker.model.parts.PartWithoutHealth
      • chuckeles.sstasker.model.parts.OxygenGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Part

    public class OxygenGenerator
extends PartWithoutHealth
    Generates oxygen on the spaceship. It is unaffected by it's health and produces a constant supply of oxygen. Required energy to function. For this it searches for generator with enough energy. It consumes energy even if it's internal storage is full.
